3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves feature extraction and clustering, which are techniques commonly used in information retrieval. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper involves clustering, which is a machine learning technique. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper involves computation of dissimilarity matrix and hierarchical clustering, which are data structures and algorithms commonly used in computer science.
